ingful tests can use an in-process Vert.x HttpServer with WebClient for GET/POST JSON, forms, multipart upload, streaming, caching, redirects, cookies, and sessions; no external service is required.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"If tests deliberately cover OAuth2WebClient, io.vertx:vertx-auth-oauth2 is an optional dependency and may need to be added, but it is not required for meaningful core web-client coverage.\",\n    \"If the runtime properties are omitted for the JDK 25 native-image run, Netty unsafe/reflection paths may fail even when JVM tests pass.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0a175f630585a4b2016a41488159dc819093d813ff49a5c4a7\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1536, "output": 818, "cacheRead": 27648, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 30002, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782663288359, "responseId": "resp_0a175f630585a4b2016a414878d94c8190bb12983e35610e6e"}, "toolResults": []}
